Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.85,0:02:21.51,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}My adolescent dreams
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.49,0:02:27.16,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}Pulling, dragged me deep
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.73,0:02:30.58,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}All my body exposed
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.94,0:02:35.88,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}Marked up by your shadows
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.65,0:02:38.62,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}Tighten up
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.64,0:02:39.67,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}Numb your senses
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.67,0:02:42.42,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}No fairness is needed for pigs
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.85,0:02:45.53,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}Laughters above
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.55,0:02:48.15,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}Playful smiles
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.17,0:02:50.75,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}Die get rolled
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.81,0:02:53.10,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}Bathe in sorrow
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.14,0:02:57.02,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}My tomorrow is built upon your flesh
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.06,0:02:58.63,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}Slay the last of your kind
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.67,0:03:06.64,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}To reclaim what's rightfully mine
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.47,0:03:02.67,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3\fs-1\pos(640,673)}Each time we'll enter
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.77,0:03:04.09,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3\fs-1\pos(640,673)}First time to make this
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.19,0:03:06.69,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3\fs-1\pos(640,673)}Final dungeon 無念な未来の
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.80,0:03:08.05,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}I have a reason
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.13,0:03:09.34,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}Don't part the rivers
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.40,0:03:12.04,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}Surround them, off with their heads
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.13,0:03:13.34,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}Christen my motive
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.38,0:03:14.64,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}First time to notice
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.66,0:03:17.31,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}Final dungeon 群れて迷おう
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.32,0:03:18.59,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}I hide among you
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.61,0:03:19.60,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}Facing my fire
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.64,0:03:23.98,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}At night I'm dreaming 永い夢の言葉
